		"description": "<p>When you select this archetype at 3rd level, you have developed the unique psionic ability to render your emotions, particularly your fury, contagious, and to project them onto others.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span></p><p>Whenever you gain rage hit points, you can use your reaction to project your rage at another creature within 20 feet.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>They either gain temporary hit points equal the number of rage hit points you just gained, or take psychic damage equal to that amount.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span></p><p>At 6th level the range of this ability increases to 30 feet, at 10th level it increases to 40ft, and at 14th level it increases to 50ft.</p>",
